{"tid":1919653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新冠肺炎疫情持續 奧組委指東京奧運或延期1至2年","createTime":"2020-03-11T02:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T02:46:11.000Z","uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e85253293fe646c374002cbf0b7c49dd549b9c","tid":1919653,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:29:28.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎蔓延全球，原定七月舉行的東京奧運未知能否如期進行。東奧25名執行委員之一的高橋治之，向美國傳媒表示，無論閉門舉行或取消，都會造成嚴重經濟損失，故若果疫情導致奧運無法按原定計劃進行，最大可能是延期1至2年。<br />\n<br />\n高橋治之表示，不認為東京奧運將會取消，因為美國所付的轉播費相當高，若果取消將為國際奧委會帶來很大麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1719960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1719960&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=bf2d7fdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1719960</a>"},{"pid":"a47dda09f90468afa6a88d0caa01c2036667dbe4","tid":1919653,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:46:11.000Z","msg":"最好延期啦"}]}